* Pentin, Edward, [http://www.ncregister.com/daily-news/inter-mirifica-and-the-changing-world-of-communication &quot;''Inter mirifica'' and the Changing World of Communication&quot;], ''[[National Catholic Register]]'', 15 Nov., 2013.
* Tanner, Norman P. The Church and the World : ''Gaudium et spes'', ''Inter mirifica''. New York: Paulist Press, 2005.

